	" is a game show video game that is based off of the short-lived game show of the same name. The rules are simple: the player known as "the One" plays a trivia game against a hundred other people known collectively as "the Mob". Whoever in the Mob answers incorrectly is eliminated from the game and the prize money amount increases. The game continues until the One either gets a question wrong, quits with their earnings, or outlasts the Mob. As the questions get harder, the One may ask for help from the Mob in a similar manner to the lifelines in 
	[em 
		"Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?
	]em
